name: Cube Fall (jt_gladden)
description:
In this game the goal is to keep the red cube (you) from hitting any of the green cubes. The longer you survive the higher your score gets and the faster the green cubes decent is. Reminds me of cube field a bit. Hopefully you can enjoy it for a few minutes at least 🙃

Leave me any feedback below but keep in mind I'm pretty new to JavaScript, web development, and 3D graphics as a whole.
